      <h2>The Token Economy</h2>
      <p>
        Effort is measured in LLM API tokens, not human-hours. The bottleneck isn't generation speed — it's review quality.<Cite id={5} author="Kahneman, Daniel" title="Thinking, Fast and Slow" source="Farrar, Straus and Giroux" year={2011} /> Kahneman's distinction between System 1 (fast, automatic) and System 2 (slow, deliberate) thinking maps directly: AI operates in System 1 mode, producing fluent text rapidly; human review is System 2, catching errors that fluency masks.
      </p>
      <div class="table-wrap">
